<Author>ff_boston
<Content>Unparalleled - Best service I have ever had in EU or US I can describe the service during my 5-days at this hotel with one word: unparalleled. From the people at the reception (Amelie, Alisa, Miguel, Fran and Daniela), all speaking perfect English and accommodating my every need, to Fran the barista, bringing me my espresso as soon as he saw me coming down in the hall in the morning, even without me asking. I could keep going, but then again I think I made my point. Extra nice, super-professional, yet never intrusive or overbearing, this is the most professional, best hotel staff I have ever ran into - and I do travel quite a bit, across the US and Europe. I wish I could get this type of treatment somewhere else, but I think it will be hard.Really, I am finicky about stuff, but these people really are a match to the superior, gorgeous design interior of the hotel hall! I will come back and recommend it to all people I know coming to Barcelona! 
