<Content>do not stay here if you speak no spanish This is a beautiful hotel,but the service is lacking if you don't speak any Spanish. Not one of the staff speaks a word of English.Consequently, we couldn't find out if the hotel has the facilities as stated on the website, reception was not aware if there is a gym/sauna, or if there is, where in the hotel it is...we couldn't get any room service, despite it supposedly being available all afternoon until 11pm.A very very disappointing experience, despite the lovely hotel building and room.I would think that a hotel that markets itself towards English speaking customers should make an effort to employ staff that have a basic understanding of the language. 
