<Author>HappyTraveler64
<Content>Nice hotel in quiet residential location I just stayed at this hotel while visiting the UPC campus which is very nearby. If you are visiting UPC, this hotel is in an outstanding location, 5 minute walk from campus. The lobby and rooms are modern and stylish. My room was not large, but it was very modern and nicely appointed. The bathroom was gorgeous. The room overall had everything I needed, including free wireless internet. The most remarkable thing about this hotel is the staff. They go out of their way to help. When I arrived, the checkin process took only moments, and almost as quickly they had brought a fresh cup of coffee to my room. At checkout, they had my luggage into a taxi for the airport within about a minute of me appearing in the lobby. They are clearly well-trained, and it was a nice experience. 
