<Content>Excellent value for money I stayed recently at this small, new hotel right in the centre of Barcelona. The biggest advantage is clearly the location. Aerobus drops one off right in front of the hotel (Gracia/Diputacio). From there Plaza Cataluna, Avda. Diagonal, Gracia etc. are in short walking distance. Apart from that one gets to stay in a very modern, nicely designed hotel with all amenities one would expect. Only downer was breakfast. But I guess for 65?/doubleroom one can live with that. 
